## Phase 14: Fill Processing

### Rejection Handling

| Rejection Code | Action | Details |
|----------------|--------|---------|
| INSUFFICIENT_MARGIN | Reduce quantity | 50% reduction |
| STOCK_HALTED | Wait and retry | 60s delay |
| PRICE_COLLAR_VIOLATION | Adjust price | Re-price order |
| CONNECTION_TIMEOUT | Exponential backoff | 5s, 10s, 30s |
| DUPLICATE_ORDER_ID | Regenerate ID | New client order ID |
| MARKET_CLOSED | Cancel | No retry |
| POSITION_LIMIT_REACHED | Escalate | Alert risk team |

